profile:
We provide professional pest control services throughout Haliburton, Bancroft, Peterborough, Lindsay and the Kawartha Lakes region.
All work is performed by government licensed personal and is fully guaranteed.
Our company was ranked #1 in Customer Satisfaction in 2008 and we strive to attain the same in 2009.
